          "goseg/broadcast/state.go"
        ],
        "evidence": [
          "goseg/broadcast/loop.go:210-213 handles buildBroadcastTickState failure, then calls `_ = stateRuntime.AddSystemTransitionError(err.Error())` and returns only the original error.",
          "goseg/broadcast/state.go:71-76 shows AddSystemTransitionError can fail (ErrBroadcastRuntimeRequired), so this path can silently lose the failure to persist transition diagnostics."
